    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/e49842d8f49475ddced011445cf87a3d.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=201 /></span><br>Year 2979, the cosmic entity &quot;IT&quot; threatens to destroy Earth. <br>Take command of the Valkyria Zenith Serenity and use all your skills to face this threat alongside your beautiful operators. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/bcf5dae3762f5ae32a4ec0a02b3e3cee.avif?t=1722951943\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras_big/bcf5dae3762f5ae32a4ec0a02b3e3cee.avif?t=1722951943 width=1170 height=658 /></span><br><strong>Save the world!</strong><br>The objective of the game is quite simple: protect Earth from the cosmic entity known as &quot;It&quot;.<br>This game is compatible with touchscreen, and it is recommended to play with a keyboard and mouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/d679625b5c0222eb0fd637158c372cf6.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Different ways to play </strong><br>On board the Valkyria, you'll find multiple operators, each with a different playing style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/d679625b5c0222eb0fd637158c372cf6.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Upgrade your ship</strong><br>The Valquiria Zenith Serenity features an onboard shop that allows you to upgrade the statistics of all your operators.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/1e5ea9fa05b2eb2289bbfbe1b7269c60.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Test your luck </strong><br>The casino module includes a small roulette wheel that allows you to exchange tickets obtained for large amounts of money. <br>(This is not a microtransaction)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/dc056ae2aa33bed0e872316881a82040.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Accelerate the growth of your relationship with the operators </strong><br>You can buy various pastries for your operators and discover a little more about them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/473fba3d6451d21bedc66f57509eb581.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125260/extras/40bc1a67c3acb1718c2f0011f012865d.avif?t=1722951943\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
